A steaming round pizza on a rustic wooden serving board, topped with glossy teriyaki-glazed chicken pieces and delicate dark green nori seaweed strips arranged in an artistic pattern, with subtle sesame seed garnish catching the light. The scene is set in a warm, intimate restaurant setting with soft amber lighting. In the background, slightly blurred, hints of both Italian wine bottles and Japanese ceramic sake cups sit side by side on weathered shelves. Steam rises gently from the pizza creating an appetizing atmosphere. Shot in photorealistic style with shallow depth of field, warm color grading emphasizing golden browns and deep greens, as if captured by a professional food photographer using natural window light mixed with warm restaurant ambiance.
